Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:04.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱花绽放之未来恋梦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.44,0:00:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天空好蓝 你露出了微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.18,0:00:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不经意的一句话使内心相系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.26,0:00:36.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚穿上的鞋  敞开门扉的后方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:43.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你重合的景色使我心动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.98,0:00:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱花绽放之未来恋梦\N加速的心跳无法压抑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.85,0:01:02.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两人共同感受  季节不断更替
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.36,0:01:10.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无可取代的瞬间\N编织着邂逅的物语
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.33,0:01:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对纷飞的樱花许下心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.31,0:01:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向前行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.24,0:01:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花盛开着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.00,0:01:53.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以因为这样就退缩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.92,0:02:04.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.40,0:02:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来似乎已经康复了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.53,0:02:22.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉让你们担心了\N（#22 美好的回忆）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.90,0:02:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据医生的说法\N是忽然出现复原征兆的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.71,0:02:34.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过会这样的原因也是不明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:37.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是悬疑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.75,0:02:40.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还是太好了 朝仓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.86,0:02:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音梦学姐 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.79,0:02:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样很难受的 美春
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.66,0:02:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音梦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之可以安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.67,0:02:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝仓今晚也休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:01.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你几乎都没睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.11,0:03:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.51,0:03:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥照顾生病的妹妹是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.68,0:03:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.29,0:03:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这么重要的时刻\N我那位神秘女郎去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.29,0:03:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚就好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:29.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美的月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.93,0:03:33.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天肯定是个好天气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.25,0:03:44.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点吓一跳对吧 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.02,0:03:51.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.69,0:03:55.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就又能一起去上学了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:57.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:03:59.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.40,0:04:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定马上就可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.41,0:04:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.55,0:04:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.95,0:04:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不走快一点又要迟到啰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.56,0:04:26.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.92,0:04:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音梦说的果然没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.46,0:04:31.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又跟平常那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:32.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音梦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.37,0:04:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赖子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.37,0:04:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么露出这种表情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.47,0:04:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.64,0:04:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要迟到啰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.25,0:04:51.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯一真是奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.32,0:04:55.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子大概又忘记写作业了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作业？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.46,0:04:59.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有这种东西么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有啊 要写两张数学讲义
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:07.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是么…这是梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:11.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的我跟赖子是同班同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.91,0:05:17.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个人要做相同的作业\N坐在同一间教室里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.68,0:05:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.35,0:05:26.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱花漂亮到让人头晕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.79,0:05:30.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯一 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.93,0:05:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好不可思议呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.64,0:05:45.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.88,0:05:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯一 纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:06:00.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事情了么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.89,0:06:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你好像一直在呻吟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赖子？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.96,0:06:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.56,0:06:13.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么请赶快换衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.63,0:06:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早餐我已经准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.54,0:06:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.04,0:06:26.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我怎么会做那种梦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且一大早就吃咖喱…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.42,0:06:37.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不爱吃么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.09,0:06:38.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我喜欢吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:39.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是虽然喜欢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.66,0:06:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.73,0:06:48.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说好吃确实是很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.10,0:06:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是赖子用大锅子\N一口气就煮了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.30,0:06:54.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每做一次就得吃好久的咖喱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:06:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.44,0:06:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:03.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚 明天跟后天的份都够
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.51,0:07:04.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.18,0:07:08.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:12.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然在这种时候不太对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.09,0:07:15.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我有个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.96,0:07:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么突然变得这么慎重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.40,0:07:20.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赖子你又不是外人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.90,0:07:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以有话直说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:25.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就是那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.47,0:07:29.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…请务必…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:31.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请给我薪水好么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.54,0:07:32.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薪水…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:37.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薪水？怎么忽然这么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.21,0:07:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们家没什么钱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.72,0:07:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.55,0:07:43.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.16,0:07:46.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.49,0:07:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要的不是钱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.56,0:07:50.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.66,0:07:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚可以跟我约会么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:07:59.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.57,0:08:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.74,0:08:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赖子那么努力练习走到户外
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.81,0:08:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那等下次放假…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.81,0:08:09.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 一定要今天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.75,0:08:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:24.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得今天的赖子有点怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.20,0:08:28.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我为什么会做那个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.04,0:08:33.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥你在想什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.97,0:08:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 是小樱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:37.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可以这样讲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.48,0:08:40.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亏人家这么担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.48,0:08:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就别担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:43.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸好音梦她…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.61,0:08:44.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她已经康复了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.85,0:08:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.62,0:08:50.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.99,0:08:53.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我当然会知道啰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:57.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 我知道哥哥的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.86,0:08:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.23,0:09:02.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天放学要直接回家喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为今晚是很重要的一夜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.24,0:09:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.37,0:09:10.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么连这个都知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就别问这么多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:16.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要对赖子温柔一点喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.52,0:09:24.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可从没让赖子吃苦过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.52,0:09:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.26,0:09:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过今晚比较特别
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.66,0:09:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不应该由我来说就是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.53,0:09:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.40,0:09:39.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.41,0:09:43.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然说不出哪里奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.54,0:09:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却感觉跟平常不太一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.68,0:09:53.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是到底是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.53,0:10:06.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌丸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是小樱安排的么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.41,0:10:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就拜托你照顾一下啰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.42,0:10:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赖子 准备好了么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:30.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯一 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:34.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样会很奇怪么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.06,0:10:38.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会的 这样很适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.43,0:10:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就出门吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.93,0:10:45.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赖子你想去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.07,0:10:48.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要去吃饭还是看电影
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.64,0:10:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去风见学园
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.31,0:10:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去纯一念的风见学园看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:11:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起走那条樱花大道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 天上好多星星呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.37,0:11:23.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.17,0:11:28.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前还那么害怕出门不是么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.31,0:11:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经练习了很多次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何况今天有纯一陪着我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.39,0:11:39.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过真的这样就好么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:40.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.52,0:11:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我的梦想就是\N跟纯一两人走在这条路上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.10,0:11:47.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦想？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.37,0:11:52.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来我看到的是赖子的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.51,0:12:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱花漂亮到让人头晕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.92,0:12:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯一 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.56,0:12:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赖子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.83,0:12:18.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好不可思议呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.33,0:12:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 赖子想要去学校
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.84,0:12:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然已经知道的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.60,0:12:28.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赖子 往这边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.21,0:12:31.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.45,0:12:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.35,0:12:40.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走这里吧 赖子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.85,0:12:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要从这里么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.26,0:12:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是我的秘密入口
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.29,0:12:51.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心 我会在这边接住你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.13,0:12:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.13,0:12:53.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.77,0:13:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:02.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么请把手给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚转学的大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:09.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.46,0:13:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是纯一的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.63,0:13:26.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯一就是在这里\N跟音梦他们一起上课呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.66,0:13:28.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不太用功就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.62,0:13:50.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是转学生鹭泽赖子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.32,0:13:55.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有很多地方不太习惯\N请大家多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.03,0:13:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.44,0:14:06.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:10.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那鹭泽的位子就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.21,0:14:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,历老师 我旁边有空位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.45,0:14:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样像不像？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:39.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,微风在窗外嬉戏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.07,0:14:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉就像是伸手可及
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.68,0:14:51.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的背好宽广
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.48,0:14:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口头禅也隐藏着体贴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.35,0:15:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光是在心中想像就受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:09.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟随着你的这个景色
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.50,0:15:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宛如飞舞在天空的鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.40,0:15:17.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是让爱悄悄进展
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.67,0:15:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何事情都办得到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.51,0:15:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想现在传达我真正的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.55,0:15:30.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宛如向下延伸的彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.55,0:15:34.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经不再迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.16,0:15:39.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴认识你  我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.68,0:15:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好怀念呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:02.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像小时候的冒险一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:03.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冒险么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.19,0:16:08.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半夜跑到学校里试胆量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.33,0:16:11.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然恐怖却也很刺激\N真的是相当有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是美好的回忆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.83,0:16:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.47,0:16:20.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快乐的时光总是过得很快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:26.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托福我也享受了美好的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:30.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天真的非常谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.48,0:16:31.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.55,0:16:33.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.92,0:16:36.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你已经敢出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如赖子也来风见学园上学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.12,0:16:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以成为真正的转学生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.36,0:16:47.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我、音梦、小樱跟杉并\N每天肯定能过得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.43,0:16:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.94,0:16:55.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:57.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.14,0:16:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都已经努力到现在了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.88,0:17:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是你却…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.38,0:17:03.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让梦想只是个梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.45,0:17:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不对 赖子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.82,0:17:08.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 我的梦想…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:10.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.52,0:17:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是没办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.09,0:17:16.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.90,0:17:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱花树就快要枯萎了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.67,0:17:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有发现么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.54,0:17:36.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初音岛的所有樱花\N都已经开始在枯萎了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了要救音梦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱才会这么决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.35,0:17:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱为了音梦…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.12,0:17:50.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音梦的病或许是因为我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.56,0:17:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我周遭所发生的一切\N都来自那棵樱花树的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.07,0:17:59.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.07,0:18:02.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是这跟赖子有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这座初音岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:09.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个少女爱上了某个少年
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她是个封闭内心的悲哀少女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.59,0:18:20.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有勇气自己向前踏出一步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:24.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赖子 你在说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.23,0:18:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她总是关在自己的房间里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.53,0:18:31.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她所看得见的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.74,0:18:35.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有从窗口看出去的些许景色
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:43.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过为了实现她的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.61,0:18:47.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有东西代替她前往外面的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.99,0:18:52.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赖子 那么你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.63,0:18:59.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于她化身成一个女仆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.06,0:19:03.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且跟少女思念的少年相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.14,0:19:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我的梦想在今天实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.64,0:19:12.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以和暗恋的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:16.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟纯一编织出美好的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.78,0:19:18.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赖子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.58,0:19:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该道别了 纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:25.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经必须要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.79,0:19:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.22,0:19:30.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过赖子就是赖子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己鼓起勇气走到这一步的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.03,0:19:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是别人正是赖子自己对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.67,0:19:38.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.50,0:19:41.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以又有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.70,0:19:44.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赖子就以鹭泽赖子的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.97,0:19:46.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟至今一样和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.74,0:19:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我们在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.48,0:19:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.52,0:19:57.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能拥有踏出这一步的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:20:02.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都来自纯一温柔的心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.59,0:20:05.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的话我也想维持现状
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.03,0:20:08.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直留在纯一的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:16.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之所以能维持现在的模样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.54,0:20:22.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因为有魔法的协助
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:30.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了 纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:31.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赖子！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.16,0:20:37.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把咖喱分装好冰起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.26,0:20:40.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要时请微波加热享用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.26,0:20:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,袜子我已经买新的了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.64,0:20:48.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时还是要换一下比较好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.20,0:20:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.57,0:20:52.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放在我这里剩下的生活费在…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.28,0:20:54.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以 赖子！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有…还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.52,0:21:01.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯一的这份心让我好感动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.32,0:21:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得到了不输给任何人\N最珍贵且美好的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我还有最后一个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.70,0:21:16.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你不要忘记我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.70,0:21:18.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.24,0:21:22.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.37,0:21:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的好喜欢你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.95,0:21:35.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.25,0:21:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赖子…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.71,0:22:01.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赖子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.84,0:22:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底跑哪儿去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.99,0:22:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.49,0:22:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样的么…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.01,0:22:30.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预告
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.64,0:22:34.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 我这么做真的对么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.24,0:22:35.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.55,0:22:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信赖子渡过了幸福的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.05,0:22:44.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且这会永远留在赖子的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.89,0:22:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.02,0:22:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么听不见别人内心的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.42,0:22:52.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像单独被留在黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.33,0:22:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来我到底该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.77,0:22:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好害怕 朝仓同学\N（#23 真诚的告白）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.68,0:23:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从掌心满溢洒落
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.05,0:23:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有着眼泪颜色的花瓣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.69,0:23:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是对风唱出摇曳的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.43,0:23:31.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天会传达到你身边么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.24,0:23:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搜寻片段的记忆之线
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.68,0:23:44.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是希望能在前方见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.08,0:23:52.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寻找小小脚印而徘徊的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.22,0:23:56.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算明知那里什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.70,0:24:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为知道我是如此珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.10,0:24:13.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使已经凋零\N仍能傲于曾经绽放而向前
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.61,0:24:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此永远地…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.98,0:24:26.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悄悄将你的存在深藏于内心
